 class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oyb1665702587872.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oyb1665702587872.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oyb1665702587872.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oyb1665702587872\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                    \n webtrigger onBlur\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This web trigger is used to program behavior when the DSP widget loses focus.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__section_w673ab1b7b1_w674ab1b7_w675ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__table_d14711e1_d14712e1_d14713e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Declaration:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104oyb1665702587872_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__codeblock_kb1_kgj_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">webtriggeronBlur\n  Optional scope block\n  Optional variables block\n  javascript\n    Javascript to implement the client-side trigger\n  endjavascript\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Parameters:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Applies to:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n This trigger is applicable only on HTML-based DSP widgets that can get and lose focus.\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__li_d44900e1_d44901e1_d44902e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"atn1718607106464.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/atn1718607106464.html\" title=\"The htmplinput widget is used to control the type and appearance of data input controls used for a field in a dynamic server page. It is mapped to the HTML &lt;input&gt; element.\">htmlinput</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__li_d44903e1_d44904e1_d44905e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bnb1665702593780.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bnb1665702593780.html\" title=\"The htmlselect widget controls the appearance of a field with a ValRep in a Dynamic Server Page, displaying it as a drop-down list or list box. It is mapped to an HTML &lt;select&gt; element. The size property determines the type of list control.\">htmlselect</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__li_d44909e1_d44910e1_d44911e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zwa1665702594248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zwa1665702594248.html\" title=\"The htmlradiogroup widget is used to display a ValRep field in a dynamic server page as a radio group with mutually exclusive options.\">htmlradiogroup</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vht1718381378389.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vht1718381378389.html\" title=\"The htmltextarea DSP widget defines the properties of a &lt;textarea&gt; input control in a Dynamic Server Page. This is used to represent a field as a multi-line field containing plain text.\">htmltextarea</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__li_d44912e1_d44913e1_d44914e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eih1718602085507.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eih1718602085507.html\" title=\"The genericHTML DSP widget can be used to define properties for any HTML element that can be bound to a field, making it possible to manipulate its attributes in ProcScript and JavaScript.\">genericHTML</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activation:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Activated when the DSP widget loses focus.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Default behavior:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Behavior upon completion:\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n None\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__section_w676ab1b7b3_w677ab1b7_w678ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d802598e198\">\n                     \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__p_d118169e1_d118170e1_d118171e1\">If defined, the onBlur trigger is fired when the user tabs or clicks away from a field in a DSP. It can be used to reverse the effects applied by the onFocus trigger.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__section_vq1_nhj_fcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d802598e207\">Example: Using OnBlur</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, the trigger prevents the user from moving to\n               another field if the entered data in the field incorrectly.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"oyb1665702587872__pre_krq_nhj_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; On ID field\nwebtrigger OnBlur\n scope\noutput\nendscope\njavascript\n //\n if (this.getError() !== null) {\n this.focus();\n }\nendjavascript\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xef1665702590289.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webtrigger onFocus</a><p>This web trigger is used to program behavior when the DSP widget gets focus as a result of user interaction.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530799\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530799\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "webtrigger onBlur Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 webtrigger onBlur This web trigger is used to program behavior when the DSP widget loses focus. Declaration: Explain this code webtriggeronBlur Optional scope block Optional variables block javascript Javascript to implement the client-side trigger endjavascript end Copy Parameters: None Applies to: This trigger is applicable only on HTML-based DSP widgets that can get and lose focus. htmlinput htmlselect htmlradiogroup htmltextarea genericHTML Activation: Activated when the DSP widget loses focus. Default behavior: None Behavior upon completion: None Description If defined, the onBlur trigger is fired when the user tabs or clicks away from a field in a DSP. It can be used to reverse the effects applied by the onFocus trigger. Example: Using OnBlur In the following example, the trigger prevents the user from moving to another field if the entered data in the field incorrectly. ; On ID field webtrigger OnBlur scope output endscope javascript // if (this.getError() !== null) { this.focus(); } endjavascript end Copy Related Links webtrigger onFocus This web trigger is used to program behavior when the DSP widget gets focus as a result of user interaction. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}